item.title: Who am I?
item.description: To try and answer this in a way that will (hopefully) make you pause for a second before you close this tab is a tedious job, to say the least. But I will do my best. I am a distinct potpourri of seemingly random interests and abilities, which nonetheless tie together into a giant connected graph at some obscure level. I am a formally trained Karnatik classical vocalist and mridangam artist.
